### Firewall 

Install ufw as root:

```
apt install ufw
ufw enable
ufw default deny incoming
ufw default allow outgoing
ufw allow ssh
```

Add NAT/masquerading to `/etc/ufw/before.rules`:

```
*nat
:POSTROUTING ACCEPT [0:0]
-A POSTROUTING -s 172.16.0.0/16 -o tun0 -j MASQUERADE
```

